title: Second Annual High School Choral Festival Slated for Oct. 21 (Kutztown University of Pennsylvania)
text: ( Source : Kutztown University of Pennsylvania ) October 14 , 2015 KUTZTOWN, Pa. - The second annual Kutztown University High School Choral Festival will take place on Wednesday, Oct. 21, from 9:30 a.m. to 11:30 a.m. in Schaeffer Auditorium .
